Package it.unipv.ingsfw.JavaBeats.dao.profile

Interface IProfileDAO

All Known Implementing Classes:
ProfileDAO
public interface IProfileDAO
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing operations related to the JBProfile entity in the database. This interface provides methods to perform Insert, Remove, Update, Get operations on User and Artist records.
